### Enhancements

* Read and cache environment specifier file contents in core conda. (#15490)

### Bug fixes

* <news item>

### Deprecations

* Mark `conda.env.env.load_file` as pending deprecation, to be removed in 27.3. (#15490)

### Docs

* <news item>

### Other

* Update `EnvironmentSpecBase` api to accept `filename` and `data` during initialization. These will populate instance variables of the same name. If not provided, the `data` variable will automatically be populated from the contents of the file specified by `filename`. (#15490)
